Package: tijolo
Version: TIJOLO_VERSION-1
Architecture: amd64
Section: editors
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/hugopl/tijolo
Depends: libc6 (>=2.31), libgtksourceview-4-0, libgit2-28, libyaml
Maintainer: Hugo Parente Lima <hugo.pl@gmail.com>
Description: Lightweight, keyboard-oriented IDE for the masses.
 A general purpose IDE written in Crystal using GTK3 with
 support for Language Server Protocol.
